        "username": "niu",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2014-05-08 02:12:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nAndreas, this patch is for chown/chgrp but not create/open. uid/gid setting on creation won't be sent to OST.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
