        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2014-05-15 02:26:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nSorry, I think my comments on the last patch were not very clear. It would be ok to send both UID and GID from the MDS to the OST with each setattr record. My main complaint is that if lod_attr_set() is setting la_uid it should also set LA_UID in la_valid, or same for la_uid and LA_UID.\n\nThe benefit of fixing this in lod_attr_set() is that this doesn't need fixes for both the OST and MDT - it fixes the problem where it starts.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
